title: Romiley & Hazel Grove Walking Club
description: The adventures of Dan and Paul within the mountainous regions of the UK.
about: The Romiley & Hazel Grove Walking Club was formed circa 2006 with just 2 members. Now 15 years on, those 2 members are still the only 2 members and that headcount looks likely to remain static. The club meets annually in September to adventure in the mountainous regions of the UK.
